{"id":73986,"type":1,"name":"薔薇のために","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/14/08/73986_Hy57I.jpg","summary":"枕野ゆりは、たった一人の身内だった祖母が亡くなり、寮からも出て行かなければならなくなり、途方に暮れていた。祖母が遺した一通の手紙から、実は母親が生きており、しかもTVや映画で活躍する女優花井しょう子だと知らされる。早速札幌にあるしょう子の自宅・花屋敷家に向かったゆりが出会ったのは、とても強烈で美形の3人の異父姉兄弟だった。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>薔薇之戀</li><li><span>册数: </span>16巻</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/10497\">吉村明美</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/6749\">小学館</a>、大然、<a href=\"/person/8359\">大然文化</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/10223\">プチコミック</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>蔷薇之恋</li><li><span>发售日: </span>1992-1998</li>","collection":{"wish":3,"collect":2},"tags":[{"name":"少女漫画","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":10497,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c9/e0/10497_prsn_iuAKa.jpg","name":"吉村明美","desc":"作者"},{"id":6749,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/ec/6749_prsn_O9b2I.jpg","name":"小学馆","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8359,"image":"","name":"台湾大然出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":10223,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/cf/c5/10223_prsn_2Qj2F.jpg","name":"プチコミック","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":126495,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d9/f4/126495_0TjA2.jpg","title":"薔薇之戀","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/126495"}],"comic":[{"id":74016,"name":"薔薇のために (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/63/55/74016_jp.jpg"},{"id":74017,"name":"薔薇のために (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/53/77/74017_jp.jpg"},{"id":74018,"name":"薔薇のために (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/d5/5c/74018_jp.jpg"},{"id":74019,"name":"薔薇のために (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/b1/64/74019_jp.jpg"},{"id":74020,"name":"薔薇のために (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/79/75/74020_jp.jpg"},{"id":74021,"name":"薔薇のために (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ee/28/74021_jp.jpg"},{"id":74022,"name":"薔薇のために (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/5f/9f/74022_jp.jpg"},{"id":74023,"name":"薔薇のために (8)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/46/bd/74023_jp.jpg"},{"id":74024,"name":"薔薇のために (9)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9a/20